  additional_info={. *Equal contribution (co-first authors)},
  abstract={An industry case study, conducted at Amazon Prime Video, on assessing the risk of software deployments using diff-aware features derived from code changes. We show how features extracted from code diffs can be used to predict the likelihood that a given deployment introduces a regression, helping teams prioritize review and testing effort.},
